snippet.title: Conception PLUS: Maidens of the Twelve Stars | PS4, Steam (PC)
snippet.description:
Conception PLUS: Maidens of the Twelve Stars is coming to PS4 on November 5, 2019! The announcement trailer reveals the voice cast and a Day 1 Edition!

Pre-order Conception PLUS: Maidens of the Twelve Stars on Amazon today:
https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07TZSMH5N/

Learn more at the official website:
http://spike-chunsoft.com/Conception_PLUS
